<plot>Lola, a factory worker, finally decides to run away from Mario, the drunk and aggressive man she loves. That same night she has a love affair with Roberto, a French rich man. Eventually they marry and have a daughter, apparently product of their first night. Four years later Mario has saved some money and begins haunting Lola in order to recover her and the girl he thinks is his daughter, not Roberto's.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?340483</url></doc>
